        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "CHAPTER three",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000001_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000001_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "Land",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000002_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000002_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "In the first watch we kept away two points and set fore and aft sail.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000002_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000002_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "It did not increase our comfort but gave us greater speed.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000002_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000002_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "I could not sleep thinking of the sore strait for our wretched ponies.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000002_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000002_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "In the morning watch the wind and sea increased and the outlook was very distressing, but at six ice was sighted ahead.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000002_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000002_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "Under ordinary conditions the safe course would have been to go about and stand to the east.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000002_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000002_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "But in our case we must risk trouble to get smoother water for the ponies.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000002_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000002_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "We passed a stream of ice over which the sea was breaking heavily and one realised the danger of being amongst loose floes in such a sea.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000002_000012",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000002_000012.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "We ran on for a bit, then stopped and lay to.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000002_000013",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000002_000013.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "Now we are lying in a sort of ice bay-there is a mile or so of pack to windward, and two horns which form the bay embracing us.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000002_000015",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000002_000015.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "As a result we are lying very comfortably.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000002_000016",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000002_000016.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "The ice is drifting a little faster than the ship so that we have occasionally to steam slowly to leeward.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "So far so good.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "From a dangerous position we have achieved one which only directly involved a waste of coal.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000003_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000003_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "The question is, which will last longest, the gale or our temporary shelter?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "Rennick has just obtained a sounding of one hundred eighty seven fathoms; taken in conjunction with yesterday's one thousand one hundred eleven fathoms and Ross's sounding of one hundred eighty, this is interesting, showing the rapid gradient of the continental shelf.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000005_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000005_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "Unfortunately we could not clear the line for the trawl-it is stowed under the fodder.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "A light dredge was tried on a small manilla line-very little result.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000006_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000006_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "There seems to be another from south but none from the direction from which the wind is now blowing.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000006_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000006_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "The wind has been getting squally: now the squalls are lessening in force, the sky is clearing and we seem to be approaching the end of the blow.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000006_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000006_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "I trust it may be so and that the New Year will bring us better fortune than the old.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "At ten p m to night as the clouds lifted to the west a distant but splendid view of the great mountains was obtained.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000008_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000008_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "Mount Sabine was one hundred ten miles away when we saw it.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "Finis nineteen ten",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "At eight a m the ship was clear of the ice and headed south with fore and aft sail set.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "Oates reports that the ponies are taking it pretty well.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000014_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000014_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "We increased to fifty five revolutions at ten a m",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000014_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000014_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "The swell is subsiding but not so quickly as I had expected.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "To night it is absolutely calm, with glorious bright sunshine.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "Several people were sunning themselves at eleven o'clock! sitting on deck and reading.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000016_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000016_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "The land is clear to night.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000016_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000016_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "Coulman Island seventy five miles west.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000017_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000017_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "Sounding at seven p m, one hundred eighty seven fathoms. Sounding at four a m, three hundred ten ,,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000018_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000018_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "Several of us drew a bucket of sea water and had a bath with salt water soap on the deck.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000018_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000018_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "The deck bathing habit has fallen off since we crossed the Antarctic circle, but Bowers has kept going in all weathers.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000021_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000021_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "With all sail set we are making very good progress.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "For the moment it doesn't look hopeful.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000024_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000024_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "We have been continuing our line of soundings.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
