    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000026_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000026_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "Alas!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000026_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000026_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "Cape Crozier with all its attractions is denied us.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000027_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000027_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "The Barrier was not more than sixty feet in height.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000027_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000027_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "From the crow's nest one could see well over it, and noted that there was a gentle slope for at least a mile towards the edge.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000027_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000027_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "The land of Black (or White?) Island could be seen distinctly behind, topping the huge lines of pressure ridges.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000028_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000028_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "The Barrier takes a sharp turn back at two or three miles from the cliffs, runs back for half a mile, then west again with a fairly regular surface until within a few hundred yards of the cliffs; the interval is occupied with a single high pressure ridge-the evidences of pressure at the edge being less marked than I had expected.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000029_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000029_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "In the angle at the corner near the cliffs Rennick got a sounding of one hundred forty fathoms and Nelson some temperatures and samples.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000030_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000030_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "Meanwhile, one of the whale boats was lowered and Wilson, Griffith Taylor, Priestley, Evans, and I were pulled towards the shore.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000030_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000030_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "The after guard are so keen that the proper boat's crew was displaced and the oars manned by Oates, Atkinson, and Cherry Garrard, the latter catching several crabs.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000031_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000031_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "On top of this old floe we saw an old Emperor moulting and a young one shedding its down.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000032_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000032_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "These Crozier cliffs are remarkably interesting.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000032_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000032_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "Bands of bright yellow occurred in the rich brown of the cliffs, caused, the geologists think, by the action of salts on the brown rock.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000032_000008",
