        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "It makes the position rather alarming when one is feeling one's way into some doubtful corner.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000037_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000037_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "What an excellent time these animals must have with thousands of penguins passing to and fro!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000039_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000039_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "From the penguin rookeries to the west it is a relentless coast with high ice cliffs and occasional bare patches of rock showing through.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000039_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000039_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "Even if landing were possible, the grimmest crevassed snow slopes lie behind to cut one off from the Barrier surface; there is no hope of shelter till we reach Cape Royds.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000040_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000040_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "Meanwhile all hands are employed making a running survey.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000040_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000040_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "I give an idea of the programme opposite.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000040_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000040_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "The Bay on the north side of Erebus is much deeper than shown on the chart.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000041_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000041_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "The sun has been obstinate all day, peeping out occasionally and then shyly retiring; it makes a great difference to comfort.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "low"
    },
