        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "Beaufort Island looks very black from the south.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000054_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000054_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "On the uniform dark reddish brown of the land can be seen numerous grey spots; these are erratic boulders of granite.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000055_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000055_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "Another group of killer whales were idly diving off the penguin rookery; an old one with a very high straight dorsal fin and several youngsters.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-low_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-3417_6522_000055_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/3417/6522/3417_6522_000055_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "We watched a small party of penguins leaping through the water towards their enemies.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
