        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3417",
        "content": "The warm glow of the sun with the keen invigorating cold of the air forms a combination which is inexpressibly health giving and satisfying to me, whilst the golden light on this wonderful scene of mountain and ice satisfies every claim of scenic magnificence.",
